____________________________________________________
Use any C++17 compatible compiler.
g++ -std=c++17 -o AirgeadApp main.cpp Application.cpp InvestmentData.cpp InvestmentCalculator.cpp ReportPrinter.cpp

To Run Program:
./AirgeadApp


How to Use
- Launch the program.

- Enter the requested investment values.

- Press Enter to continue.

- Review the two generated reports.

- Choose whether to run another simulation.